text: Agneta Schützer also with surname Danielsson (born October 1946) is a Swedish former long track speed skater, who was active in the 1960s. Schützer represented her nation at the World Allround Speed Skating Championships for Women in 1966, finishing 31st overall. She also competed at other international competitions. Between 1962 and 1969 she competed seven times at the Swedish Allround Championships, with her best result in 1967 and 1968 finishing 6th. == Records== === Personal records === ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Swedish female speed skaters Category:Living people
